POWER BI DENEB - SINGLE-CANVAS VEGA DASHBOARD

This version contains no Vega-Lite vconcat and cannot create duplicate
height signals.

DATA SOURCE
Import: AIA PowerBI One Sheet Database.xlsx
Sheet: PowerBI_Data

ADD THESE FIELDS TO DENEB VALUES
- Company
- ProductName
- IndexName
- Currency
- CohortNo
- ParticipationRate
- CapRate
- FloorRate
- Date
- Price
- IndexNormalized
- ProductValue

IMPORTANT DENEB SETUP
1. Create a new Deneb visual.
2. Add all 12 fields above.
3. Choose Create new specification.
4. Choose Vega, not Vega-Lite.
5. Choose Empty.
6. Paste only the JSON below.
7. Select Apply.

